snippet.textDisplay:
Sajjad Ali's voice is quite sweet and his notes are flawless..Have been listening to his Coke Studio songs for over a decade. Songs like Tum Naraz Ho, Rone Na Diya, Rang Laga (with Sanam Marvi), KirKir KirKir, Tera Naam etc. Have enjoyed some of the finest bubbling moments and ruminative sessions of my previous decade through his songs. Glad to listen to this new song "Chal Chaliye".
Much Love!!
